  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Demonk is a cooperative horror experience for 1–4 players, where you take on the sacred role of Slavic monks — trained in the forgotten art of dealing with the dead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your mission: communicate with ancient spirits, uncover their stories, and choose whether to banish them... or negotiate for peace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set in a world deeply rooted in Slavic mythology, every encounter is a test of faith, logic, and trust between players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Success brings reward — money, relics, and reputation. But failure? That may cost your soul.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you find harmony with the beyond… or will the darkness consume you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>THERE IS AN APPROACH TO EVERYONE, POSSIBLY THROUGH FOOD</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3635380/extras/b998b376f2cc36a642c6f8bddec35342.avif?t=1749138342\" width=620 height=270 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>AND POSSIBLY THROUGH BONES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3635380/extras/076f47df0216b5ad0eb593e4ac02b3eb.avif?t=1749138342\" width=620 height=270 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Demonk is a cooperative horror experience for 1–4 players, where you take on the sacred role of Slavic monks — trained in the forgotten art of dealing with the dead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your mission: communicate with ancient spirits, uncover their stories, and choose whether to banish them... or negotiate for peace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set in a world deeply rooted in Slavic mythology, every encounter is a test of faith, logic, and trust between players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Success brings reward — money, relics, and reputation. But failure? That may cost your soul.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you find harmony with the beyond… or will the darkness consume you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>THERE IS AN APPROACH TO EVERYONE, POSSIBLY THROUGH FOOD</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3635380/extras/b998b376f2cc36a642c6f8bddec35342.avif?t=1749138342\" width=620 height=270 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>AND POSSIBLY THROUGH BONES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3635380/extras/076f47df0216b5ad0eb593e4ac02b3eb.avif?t=1749138342\" width=620 height=270 /></span></p>",
